        "subject": "LU-17860 build: systemd unit libpath changes",
        "message": "LU-17860 build: systemd unit libpath changes\n\nUbuntu 24.04 changed the default systemd unit library path\nfrom: lib/systemd/system\n  to: usr/share/bash-completion/completions\nMake debian/lustre-client-utils.install.in and\n     debian/lustre-server-utils.install.in\nTo use configure AC_SUBST variables as the systemd library\npath is determined during configure.\n\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-12349\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: Ibe7c1c9b2e405462ace0851b84c8686d8094a74e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
